# Routing & Navigation

## React Router v6
- Use `useNavigate()`, `useLocation()`, `Navigate` for programmatic navigation
- Routes defined in Navigation or App; screens map to paths

## Protected Routes
- Redirect to `/login` when `!currentUser && !loading`
- Admin routes: check `admin` or `developer` on user doc before rendering
- Use `<Navigate to="..." replace />` for redirects

## Navigation Component
- Central nav in `components/common/Navigation.js`
- Use `Link` or `useNavigate` for internal links; avoid raw `<a>` for SPA routes
